      <title>英国银行被勒令开始对私募股权风险进行压力测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-banks-told-to-start-stress-testing-private-equity-exposure-by-bank-of-england</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行发现许多英国银行无法衡量其对私募股权巨头及其投资组合公司的风险敞口，并命令它们开始对这些关系进行压力测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-banks-told-to-start-stress-testing-private-equity-exposure-by-bank-of-england</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
